      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, iterative convergence monitoring to residual < 1e-5 is sufficient; formal solver error quantification not required.",
      "rationale": "Residuals monitored to < 1e-6 for all transport equations. Mass imbalance < 0.01%. Iterative convergence criterion met; formal numerical solver error quantification scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3."
    },
