    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Discretization error factor exceeds requirement (achieved level 3 vs. required level 2), providing additional confidence. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts NIH within 12.4% of experimental data across the full COU operating envelope. RH index criterion (RH < 1) satisfied at all 5 operating points. Model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
